<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior lab}
<A>__{rheya is on the ground, convulsing. beside her is a small steel drum, which is spilling a strange looking liquid that solidifies and vaporizes with a smoky hiss. kelvin moves to rheya and is startled to see that half of her face and throat are burned away not melted as in a fire, but merely eaten cleanly away. he picks her up.}
<L>__{interior corridor}
<A>__{kelvin is carrying rheya. snow sticks his head out of a passing room.}
