<A>__{rheya is shaking much harder now, kelvin tries to hold her still, but she's too strong. he stands, reluctantly, and watches her.}
<C>__{snow}
<D>__{what happens if she comes back? is that polygamy? and even if you could take her home, how would you get her through? you think they're not going to notice her?}
<A>__{rheya is shaking violently now, as if a rippling rhythmic force were coursing through her. snow, as he looks dispassionately on the two of them:}
<C>__{snow}
<D>__{i never get used to them, these... "resurrections".}
<A>__{he leaves. rheya continues her process of "waking up" it's violent, even sexual. she spasms to a peak of some sort, and then slowly returns to normal. kelvin puts his hand on her forehead. she gradually begins to open her eyes. she looks at kelvin. it takes her a moment to realize she shouldn't be seeing him; she shouldn't be seeing anything. she should be dead. she begins to cry.}
